Build:

    (Gnu make is recommended.)

    make
    sudo make install

Run:
    Terminal 1:
        ./test

    Terminal 2:
        for dtrace:
            sudo ./run.d

        for systemtap:
            sudo ./run.stp

Tested on the following systems:

    * Solaris 11 Express 2010_11 (i386)
    * Fedora 17 Linux (x86_64)

